# =============================================================================
# PeerTutor — Production reference (do not commit real .env.production)
#
# Production config is driven by:
#   - GitHub Actions secrets → CD deploys frontend to S3 + Lambda functions
#   - Terraform variables → Lambda environment variables
# =============================================================================

# ── GitHub Actions secrets (CD) — Lambda environment ─────────────────────────
# SENTRY_DSN
# SMTP_HOST, SMTP_PORT, SMTP_USER, SMTP_PASS, SMTP_FROM_EMAIL, SMTP_FROM_NAME
# SUPER_ADMIN_EMAIL
# GOOGLE_CALENDAR_CLIENT_EMAIL, GOOGLE_CALENDAR_PRIVATE_KEY, GOOGLE_CALENDAR_ID
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (optional)

# ── Frontend build (same repo secrets) ───────────────────────────────────────
# VITE_API_URL          (API Gateway URL from terraform output)
# VITE_COGNITO_USER_POOL_ID, VITE_COGNITO_CLIENT_ID, VITE_AWS_REGION
# VITE_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY (optional)
# VITE_SENTRY_DSN       (optional)

# ── AWS (Terraform outputs → GitHub) ────────────────────────────────────────
# S3_BUCKET, CLOUDFRONT_DISTRIBUTION_ID
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID, AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY, AWS_REGION
# LAMBDA_DEPLOY_BUCKET, LAMBDA_PREFIX

# ── Runbooks ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# docs/runbooks/token-and-key-rotation.md
# docs/runbooks/app-check-and-waf.md
